      "description": "<h5>(EXOSKELETON AND MECHA ONLY)</h5><p>While driving this <strong>personal vehicle</strong>, you gain a +2 bonus to Defense and a +2 bonus to Magic Defense. Additionally, this weapon module <strong>does not</strong> count as a “weapon”: instead, it counts as an equipped <strong>shield</strong>. This module <strong>cannot</strong> be equipped in your <strong>main hand slot</strong>, unless you have acquired the <strong>Dual Shieldbearer</strong> Skill (see <strong>Core Rulebook</strong>, page <strong>197</strong>). If you have, your <strong>Twin Shields</strong> deal 2 extra damage (this is cumulative if you have two <strong>Shield modules</strong> enabled at the same time).</p>",
